data.description: Welcome To Biltmore Shores. Calling All Boaters Looking for Sunrise Views. 54' Navy Bulkhead On Sought After Deep Grand Canal. Enjoy Beautiful Views of The Great South Bay From Your Custom Eat In Kitchen w/Wall Of Windows, Granite Counters, Pot Filler & Gas Cooking. Primary EnSuite with New Full Bath w/Double Vanity, Pocket Doors To A Closet Like No Other & French Doors Leading To Deck. Brand New Electric Panel. New Central Air & Water Heater. Energy Efficient Home w/26 Solar Panels To Be Assumed by Purchaser. Only $180 (once paid off, PSEG Approx $20/Mo). Fireplace In Den. Part Garage w/My "Q" Opener. Great Curb Appeal W/Paver Driveway & Brand New Handrail On Custom Dual Entry. Fiberglass Deck Extends Entire Width of Home W/Stairs To Patio & Fenced Yard. Flood Insurance Required. Tax Grievance Filed. New 2023 Survey. Ahoy!!
